<i>The Times of India</i>. 10 June 2012<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">21 July</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Times+of+India&amp;rft.atitle=Mustard+oil+has+health+risks&amp;rft.date=2012-06-10&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Farticles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com%2F2012-06-10%2Fdelhi%2F32155329_1_mustard-erucic-acid-cooking-oils&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3A1998+Delhi+oil+poisoning\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-court-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-court_5-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2008-11-27/delhi/27899854_1_mustard-oil-argemone-food-inspector\">\"Trader gets 2 years' RI for selling adulterated mustard oil\"</a>. <i>The Times of India</i>. 27 November 2008<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">21 July</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Times+of+India&amp;rft.atitle=Trader+gets+2+years%27+RI+for+selling+adulterated+mustard+oil&amp;rft.date=2008-11-27&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Farticles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com%2F2008-11-27%2Fdelhi%2F27899854_1_mustard-oil-argemone-food-inspector&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3A1998+Delhi+oil+poisoning\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<p><span id=\"coordinates\" class=\"metadata coord-missing\"></span>\n</p>\n<div role=\"navigation\" class=\"navbox\" aria-labelledby=\"Food_safety\" style=\"padding:3px\"><table class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-